message.body: Oh my goodness Sofie I just woke up!! I fell asleep last night before setting my alarm, I still wasn't feeling well and I was so exhausted.
I have a short meeting for a job in a bit. Let me call you after I shower
Oh Fatema I love you but i have to work I am feeling very stressed
Oh my darling i understand. I'm sorry I missed Skype time this morning. Your work will get done sof. Love you
